sequenceDiagram
    actor Admin
    participant Frontend as Frontend React
    participant Gateway as API Gateway
    participant Catalog as Catalog Service
    participant Cloud as Cloudinary
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    Admin->>Frontend: Remplit formulaire + sélectionne image
    Frontend->>Gateway: POST /api/upload (multipart/form-data)
    Gateway->>Catalog: Proxy requête
    Catalog->>Cloud: Upload image
    Cloud-->>Catalog: {url: "https://res.cloudinary.com/..."}
    Catalog-->>Frontend: {imageUrl}

    Frontend->>Gateway: POST /api/plats
    Note right of Frontend: {nom, description, prix, categoryId, imageUrl, allergènes[]}
    Gateway->>Catalog: Proxy requête (JWT vérifié, rôle ADMIN)
    Catalog->>Catalog: Validation des données (Zod)
    Catalog->>DB: INSERT INTO plats
    DB-->>Catalog: Plat créé
    Catalog->>DB: INSERT INTO plat_allergens
    DB-->>Catalog: Allergènes associés
    Catalog-->>Gateway: {plat créé}
    Gateway-->>Frontend: 201 Created
    Frontend-->>Admin: Notification de succès
